{
  "stem": "3933.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when they pull down his panties, and that is going to be the end of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then this Musha who is in Israel, she was by herself, and she was very famous, very rich girl.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she got lots of dollars to save herself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she got a different kind of time to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not a quarter what I was through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We talk about it with her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, when I stayed with my family and then the Germans were going, they were-- we were told OK, they were killed over there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, prisoners-- Russian prisoners of war, because the war started with the Russians, as you know, people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The war-- in '41, '39 now, no, was a pact. '41 was the start of the war of the Russians with the Germans, as you know that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know nothing of what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We find out later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One say this, and we got still a little hope-- maybe they put him into a camp, and they were working.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They will give them-- use of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They will have use of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, we-- I was glad I avoided this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't know for how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we went, pushed into this ghetto-- into this Dzielnica, into this Judenviertel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a small part that left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how many-- thousands?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Must be very small part after the Sosenki, the bulk of the Jews were already killed, this was the bulk, this is in the history.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I've read a lot of them run away to Russia, and the ones who were remaining was in the dzielnica, in the Judenviertel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went on with our lives, we were-- we were going on with our lives.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started to work for the Germans, I worked already-- I cleaned.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
